### Variables
@baseUrl = https://qjfygjtondljywhbqbfj.supabase.co/functions/v1
@authToken = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Test 1 - Ajouter un service à un événement (cas nominal)
POST {{baseUrl}}/services-add-service-to-event
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event_id": "event-uuid-here",
  "service_id": "service-uuid-here",
  "provider_id": "provider-uuid-here",
  "quantity": 1,
  "unit_price": 2000000,
  "configuration": {
    "menu_type": "premium",
    "guest_count": 150
  }
}

### Test 2 - Ajouter un service avec prix par défaut
POST {{baseUrl}}/services-add-service-to-event
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event_id": "event-uuid-here",
  "service_id": "service-uuid-here",
  "quantity": 2
}

### Test 3 - Erreur: event_id manquant
POST {{baseUrl}}/services-add-service-to-event
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "service_id": "service-uuid-here"
}

### Test 4 - Erreur: service déjà ajouté
POST {{baseUrl}}/services-add-service-to-event
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event_id": "event-uuid-here",
  "service_id": "already-added-service-uuid"
}

### Test 5 - Erreur: service inactif
POST {{baseUrl}}/services-add-service-to-event
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event_id": "event-uuid-here",
  "service_id": "inactive-service-uuid"
}

